課程概述 Course Description
       The course focuses on the basic ability of academic writing. The contents include research questions, literature reading and integration, thesis organization and writing, research grant, and paper publication. The objectives include: (1) using databases and fining literature, (2) papers reading and note-taking, (3) articles framework and writing, (4) research grant writing, and (5) article publication.  

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Understand  and apply regression analysis Familiarize software useInterpret and present statistical analyses Undsertand and apply statistical thinking 

